## Executive Summary

The Universal Consciousness Shield (UCS) Engine has been successfully integrated with AISI's ControlArena framework, demonstrating that internal ethical reasoning mechanisms can work alongside external monitoring systems. This integration proves the technical viability of the UCS approach and readiness for empirical evaluation.

